* Deploy Bundle
** Command
***_ databricks bundle deploy
** Target Selection
***_ Default target (no flag)
***_ -t dev or -t prod
** What Happens
***_ New resources: created
***_ Existing resources: updated
***_ Removed resources: deleted
** State Tracking
***_ State stored in workspace
***_ Unique per bundle+target+user
** CI/CD
***_ --auto-approve flag
***_ Skips confirmation prompts
@endmindmap
